  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a cold continental buffet breakfast and hot options including eggs and omelettes cooked to order each morning.</p>
<p>The evening meal consists of <span class="font-size-16 m-font-size-13">soup, starter, main course, cheese and dessert</span><span class="font-size-16 m-font-size-13">.</span> <span>The ingredients are fresh, seasonal and traditional, the dishes on offer are inspired by global flavours and the Savoyard surroundings. Savoyard specialities are also available - this includes soup, Savoyard speciality dish and dessert (additional fees may apply).</span></p>
<p><span>Early evening meals are available for children from 6.30pm.</span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Years Eve gala meals are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
